<section id="item-1" class="guide-section">
  <h2 class="section-title">Introduction</h2>
  <img src="/assets/img/Custom/Banner.png" alt="Custom Map Dubs banner" width="6230" height="2690" fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" />
  <p>
    This project changes the audio of some Black Ops III Custom Maps to use
    Black Ops II dubs, for versions recreated by the community.
  </p>
  <p>
    This guide explains how to install the available audio packs.
  </p>
</section>

